---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import ButtonLink from "../components/ButtonLink.astro";
---

<Base title="talks">
  <fieldset>
    <legend>Transforming Wholesale with AI</legend>
    <label>Waterloo & Toronto Tech Week 2025 (Waterloo & Toronto, Canada)</label>
    <p>
      Hosted both on Toronto and Waterloo and recorded on the Faire Wholesale YouTube channel. I present my work on
      AI-powered search and developer platform to support user-facing AI at Faire, including our Burrito architecture to
      embed Python into our Kotlin ecosystem and the requirements of real-time user-facing LLM-powered apps.
    </p>
    <div class="actions">
      <ButtonLink href="https://youtu.be/QOMYC425_bP">Video</ButtonLink>
      <ButtonLink
        href="https://craft.faire.com/transforming-wholesale-with-ai-the-sequel-now-with-more-agents-9542f257dd45"
        >Blog post</ButtonLink
      >
    </div>
  </fieldset>
  <fieldset>
    <legend>Flame 3D – Hands-On Workshop</legend>
    <label>Flutter & Friends 2025 (Stockholm, Sweden)</label>
    <p>
      90-minute workshop (with <a href="https://github.com/wolfenrain/">Jochum van der Ploeg</a>) where we introduce
      flame_3d from scratch (coordinate systems, camera/projection, meshes/materials, lights and skeletal animation) and
      guide attendees through building a small third-person 3D platformer in Flutter.
    </p>
    <div class="actions">
      <ButtonLink href="https://www.flutterfriends.dev/speakers">Event</ButtonLink>
      <ButtonLink href="https://github.com/bluefireteam/flutter_and_friends_2025_flame_3d_workshop_template">
        Slides & Code
      </ButtonLink>
    </div>
  </fieldset>
  <fieldset>
    <legend>3D Game Development with Flutter & Flame</legend>
    <label>Flutter & Friends 2024 (Stockholm, Sweden)</label>
    <p>
      Main-stage talk focusing on practical patterns for 3D game development in Flutter using Flame (scene graph, camera
      control, assets and ergonomics).
    </p>
    <div class="actions">
      <ButtonLink
        href="https://medium.com/antigua-mobile/a-flutter-journey-through-stockholm-flutter-friends-2024-6ffc33848f81"
        >Recap</ButtonLink
      >
      <ButtonLink href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zOP3L5B0O0c">Video</ButtonLink>
    </div>
  </fieldset>
  <fieldset>
    <legend>3D Games With Flame</legend>
    <label>Fluttercon USA 2024 (New York, USA)</label>
    <p>
      Conference talk live in Fluttercon NY, sister talk to the one for Flutter & Friends. I show how Impeller / GPU
      access unlocks 3D techniques in Flame, walk through a demo game, and discuss performance pitfalls.
    </p>
    <div class="actions">
      <ButtonLink href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dpg7-GCHs3w">Video</ButtonLink>
    </div>
  </fieldset>
  <fieldset>
    <legend>Flame and (Pseudo)-3D</legend>
    <label>Fluttercon EU 2023 / droidcon Berlin (Berlin, Germany)</label>
    <p>
      Talk on how to make games feel 3D even when the platform doesn’t yet expose full 3D APIs. I cover
      ray-tracing-inspired tricks, Doom-like engines, 2.5D perspectives and integration with Flame. In a sense, a
      prelude for all the work Impeller allowed us later on.
    </p>
    <div class="actions">
      <ButtonLink href="https://www.droidcon.com/2023/08/06/flame-and-pseudo-3d/">Session page</ButtonLink>
    </div>
  </fieldset>
  <fieldset>
    <legend>Building Games Using Flame</legend>
    <label>Flutter Europe 2020 (Warsaw, Poland)</label>
    <p>
      Co-presented with <a href="https://github.com/renancaraujo">Renan C. Araújo</a>, teaching the basics of game
      loops, components and performance in Flame.
    </p>
    <div class="actions">
      <ButtonLink href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sFpjEH-ok2s">Video</ButtonLink>
    </div>
  </fieldset>
  <fieldset>
    <!-- cspell:ignore Construindo Jogos usando -->
    <legend>Construindo Jogos usando Flame</legend>
    <label>Flutter Talks Brazil 2019 (São Paulo, Brazil)</label>
    <p>
      Portuguese-language talk “Building games using Flame”, focused on how to architect and ship a simple 2D game with
      Flame and Flutter.
    </p>
    <div class="actions">
      <ButtonLink href="https://www.fluttertalks.com.br/#ts-schedule">Schedule</ButtonLink>
    </div>
  </fieldset>
  <fieldset>
    <legend>Flamecon Talks</legend>
    Over the years I presented on a myriad of online Flame conferences (Flamecon) to share with the community new and exciting
    features we worked on.
    <div class="actions">
      <ButtonLink href="https://www.youtube.com/@FlameEngineDev">YouTube</ButtonLink>
    </div>
  </fieldset>
</Base>
